25
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:48,719
Neil deGrasse Tyson thinks facts are not dependent on politics,

26
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:51,760
but should be established with a scientific method,

27
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:56,000
a process of finding the truth through testing and experimentation.

28
