and then you regurgitate that for an exam.

60
00:03:56,960 --> 00:04:00,560
That's an aspect of science, but it's not the most important part of science.

61
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:04,159
The most important part of science is knowing how to question things,

62
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:11,360
and knowing when an answer has emerged that represents an objective truth about this world.

63
