Neil says that science is taught by encouraging students to regurgitate facts,

64
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:20,560
to repeat information without properly understanding it.

65
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:26,400
Knowledge is important, but what's also needed is a questioning attitude that can recognize

66
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:30,080
objective truth, a truth about the natural world,

67
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:34,960
which is not influenced by human bias, opinions, or emotion.

68
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:39,520
Without that, anyone is free to call whatever they like a fact,

69
00:04:39,599 --> 00:04:41,599
which only leads to chaos.

70
00:04:41,599 --> 00:04:45,839
Right, no matter how hard I believe the moon is made of cheese,

71
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:49,680
